verbose_text: The results of Annexin V assay demonstrated that the overexpression of miR-183 significantly induced the apoptosis of ESCs (P < 0.05), and that the apoptotic rate was decreased when miR-183 was inhibited (P < 0.05) (XREF_FIG).
evidence: Annexin V assay demonstrated that the overexpression of miR-183 significantly induced the apoptosis
